message.body: Hey! No rush, but I just want to double check - you haven't paid me back for thanksgiving driving yet, right?
Yeah I did. I gave you money the day we got back, if I remember correctly. I'm not sure if Alejandra did and I think Julianne almost definitely didn't because she beer has cash, but I know I did.
Ok that's cool. Sorry for forgetting. And they both did later so we are all set!
Oh cool haha. Yeah no problem :) how much do you want for driving one way next weekend? I should go to the ATM.
I'm driving you one way right?
Hahaha cool sounds good. I'll let him knows
What where was autocorrect to save you haha
Haha I know, it let me down...
